title: Stevie Ray Vaughan - The King's Head (1980; 2013) [FLAC]
description:
Legendary radio broadcast recording from The Kings Head Inn, a tiny venue popular with students near the Old Dominion University campus, in Norfolk, Virginia, that could accommodate barely 100 people.

2013 CD release of a live broadcast by WNOR FM99, July 22, 1980
